==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Argentous
<hw>Ar*gen"tous</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>Of, pertaining to, or containing, silver; -- said of certain silver
compounds in which silver has a higher proportion than in argentic
compounds; <as>as, <ex>argentous</ex> chloride</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Argentry</ent>⟦br⟧
